metadata.name: Ghost
metadata.description:
Ghost The Floating Goddess in Ghana. Silka creates a captivating visual for her latest music.

Ghost was a download I received while visiting Gold Coast Ghana, and traveling through the "Door of no Return." The feelings conjured up were of great gratitude for my ancestors. I am on this earth to reclaim all that was taken, and return  through the "Door if no Return" a liberated African.
